Definition: medium-sized shrubby tree of South Africa having thick leathery evergreen leaves and white or pink flowers and globose usually two-seeded purplish black fruits
Synonyms: poison_arrow_plant, Acocanthera_oblongifolia, Acocanthera_spectabilis, shrub, genus_Acocanthera, m, medium-sized, shrubby, tree, of, South, Africa, having, thick, leathery, evergreen, leaves, and, white, or, pink, flowers, globose, usually, two-seeded, purplish, black, fruits
Category: noun.plant
